---
import DocsLayout from '../../layouts/DocsLayout.astro';
---

<DocsLayout title="Migration Validation" description="Post-import validation and rollback runbook for migration operations.">
  <h1>Migration Validation</h1>
  <p style="color: var(--color-text-2); font-size: 1.1rem; margin-bottom: 32px;">
    Use this playbook after Coolify, Dokploy, or Docker Compose imports.
  </p>

  <h2>Required sequence</h2>
  <ol>
    <li>Capture pre-migration baseline</li>
    <li>Run dry-run import and compare expected counts</li>
    <li>Run apply import and verify object creation</li>
    <li>Run post-import functional checks per deployment</li>
    <li>Run rollback rehearsal in staging</li>
    <li>Run security audit and sign-off</li>
  </ol>

  <h2>Security gate</h2>
  <pre><code style="font-family: var(--font-mono);">./scripts/security-audit.sh</code></pre>

  <h2>Sign-off fields</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Source platform</li>
    <li>Dry-run and apply results</li>
    <li>Functional verification summary</li>
    <li>Rollback rehearsal result</li>
    <li>Residual risk and approver</li>
  </ul>
</DocsLayout>
